| `src/core/audit/audit-chain-contract.ts` | 18 | `Math.imul(31, h) + s.charCodeAt(i) | 0` (DJB2 variant) | NEEDS_REVIEW |
| `src/core/smartlink/smartlink.nattimer.ts` | 105 | `Math.imul(h, 0x01000193)` (FNV-1a) | NEEDS_REVIEW |

